  "id": "chattodiscord",
  "name": "ChatToDiscord",
  "author": "eDroiid",
  "description": "send messages from your PMMP server to Discord",
  "readme_markdown": "<h1>\n<a id=\"user-content-chattodiscord\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#chattodiscord\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>ChatToDiscord</h1>\n<p>send messages from your PMMP server to Discord</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://poggit.pmmp.io/ci/eDroiid/ChatToDiscord/ChatToDiscord\"><img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/a0ad907b4348695df3d2c2a0c5f879bccac76a55/68747470733a2f2f706f676769742e706d6d702e696f2f63692e62616467652f6544726f6969642f43686174546f446973636f72642f43686174546f446973636f7264\" alt=\"Poggit-CI\" data-canonical-src=\"https://poggit.pmmp.io/ci.badge/eDroiid/ChatToDiscord/ChatToDiscord\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<h1>\n<a id=\"user-content-setting-it-up\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#setting-it-up\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>Setting It Up</h1>\n<ol>\n<li>Download from <a href=\"https://poggit.pmmp.io/ci/eDroiid/ChatToDiscord/ChatToDiscord\">Poggit</a>.</li>\n<li>Add plugin to your <code>plugins</code> folder.</li>\n<li>Start and stop your server (so config is created).</li>\n<li>Open <code>plugins\\ChatToDiscord\\config.yml</code> and start customizing.</li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li>add your webhooks <code>webhooks: ['https://discordapp.com/api/webhooks/123/456789']</code>. <a href=\"https://support.discordapp.com/hc/en-us/articles/228383668-Intro-to-Webhooks\">How do I get a webhook?</a> (skip the Github Integration at the end of the article)</li>\n<li>change the username <code>username: 'My Server'</code>.</li>\n<li>change the avatar/icon <code>avatar: 'http://example.com/myserverslogo.png'</code>.</li>\n<li>change the format <code>message_format: '{player} said {message}'</code>.</li>\n</ul>\n<ol start=\"5\">\n<li>Save <code>plugins\\ChatToDiscord\\config.yml</code>.</li>\n<li>Restart your server</li>\n</ol>\n<h1>\n<a id=\"user-content-my-setup\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#my-setup\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>My Setup</h1>\n<p>Config:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/788d336cf1f7b6f404692a161b239c41e2d9041a/687474703a2f2f7075752e73682f77435455732f326665313733376465642e706e67\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/788d336cf1f7b6f404692a161b239c41e2d9041a/687474703a2f2f7075752e73682f77435455732f326665313733376465642e706e67\" alt=\"\" data-canonical-src=\"http://puu.sh/wCTUs/2fe1737ded.png\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>Discord:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/509d277544cbaa269009e91f1832c54ed17b0c0e/687474703a2f2f7075752e73682f77435457592f373335333566623933312e706e67\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/509d277544cbaa269009e91f1832c54ed17b0c0e/687474703a2f2f7075752e73682f77435457592f373335333566623933312e706e67\" alt=\"\" data-canonical-src=\"http://puu.sh/wCTWY/73535fb931.png\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<h1>\n<a id=\"user-content-to-do\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#to-do\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>To Do</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>[x] Add async so it doesn't lag main thread</li>\n<li>[x] Add multiple webhook support</li>\n<li>[ ] Add ability to send messages of events</li>\n<li>on join</li>\n<li>on quit</li>\n<li>on death</li>\n</ul>\n<script defer src=\"https://static.cloudflareinsights.com/beacon.min.js/v8c78df7c7c0f484497ecbca7046644da1771523124516\" integrity=\"sha512-8DS7rgIrAmghBFwoOTujcf6D9rXvH8xm8JQ1Ja01h9QX8EzXldiszufYa4IFfKdLUKTTrnSFXLDkUEOTrZQ8Qg==\" data-cf-beacon='{\"version\":\"2024.11.0\",\"token\":\"508eb1d242ef46b690a0886422106e77\",\"r\":1,\"server_timing\":{\"name\":{\"cfCacheStatus\":true,\"cfEdge\":true,\"cfExtPri\":true,\"cfL4\":true,\"cfOrigin\":true,\"cfSpeedBrain\":true},\"location_startswith\":null}}' crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script>",
